<figureCitation box="[606,741,1284,1311]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="27.[189,232,1894,1920]" captionTargetBox="[218,1370,265,1861]" captionTargetId="figure@27.[203,1383,250,1871]" captionTargetPageId="27" captionText="Fig. 7. A, C, E. Melanostoma fasciatum (Macquart, 1850), ♂ (AM_K407062). A. Dorsal view. C. Lateral view. E. Head and thorax, lateral view. B, D. Melanostoma univittatum (Wiedemann, 1824), ♂ (ZFMK-DIP-00019737). B. Dorsal view. D. Lateral view. F. Melanostoma apicale Bigot, 1884, ♀ (ZFMK-DIP-00019781), lateral view. Scale bars: A–D, F = 1 mm; E = 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3814073" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3814073/files/figure.png" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">Fig. 7C, E</figureCitation>
